Point,is,a,DNS,hosting,service,that,hosts,more,than,domains,for,thousands,of,users,around,the,world,It,provides,a,single,interface,from,which,users,can,manage,all,of,their,domains,and,it,lets,users,share,domain,access,with,their,teams,and,customers,PointDNS,includes,tools,for,setting,up,permanent,HTTP,redirects,and,e,mail,forwarding,and,it,allows,users,to,add,or,replicate,an,unlimited,number,of,records,to,their,domains,The,PointDNS,API,allows,users,to,integrate,the,management,of,their,DNS,into,other,applications,and,systems